  "runtime_owner": "Config, EXCLUSIVELY. Every Config property is an os.getenv() evaluated PER ACCESS (uncached). There is no runtime handoff to Settings \u2014 Settings.runtime_load has zero callers (INV-05, Cycle 2).",
